# =============================================================================
# STRICT ALLOWLIST .gitignore
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Ignore EVERYTHING by default, then re-include only the source the editor needs
# to run. Consequence: anything generated on first run/build, any dev tooling,
# any captured/game-derived data, and any original game bytes are NEVER uploaded
# -- even by accident. To ship a new top-level file/dir, add an explicit `!`.
# NOTE: .gitignore has NO inline comments -- keep every `#` on its own line.
# =============================================================================

# ignore everything at the repo root
/*

# re-include the source folders the editor actually needs
!/studio/
!/core/
!/tiles/
!/patcher/
!/examples/
!/.github/

# re-include top-level docs / config
!/README.md
!/NOTICE.md
!/THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.txt
!/LICENSE
!/requirements.txt
!/.gitignore

# re-include ONLY the APK signer (Apache-2.0, required to build); nothing else
# in vendor/ is tracked
!/vendor/
/vendor/*
!/vendor/uber-apk-signer.jar

# strip generated files / OS junk INSIDE the re-included folders
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.DS_Store
.DS_Store
*.bak
*.bak2
*.log

# prebuilt native libs are generated by the NDK; ignore the folder by default
# (the release .so is re-included at the bottom so users can build without the NDK)
core/native/prebuilt/
jre/

# NEVER commit game bytes / binaries / dev rigs (belt & suspenders, any path).
# The mod ships ONLY user-authored content; the game is supplied at runtime.
**/*.so
**/*.so.src
**/*.so.patched
**/*.bin
**/*.xapk
**/*.apk
**/*.apk.idsig
**/*.unity3d
**/*.unity3d.mod
**/*.dat
**/global-metadata.dat
**/node_modules/
**/*.node
**/frida-server

# ...but DO ship the RELEASE prebuilt native lib + the libmain DT_NEEDED diff, so
# users can build without the NDK or LIEF. Debug builds (-dbg) stay ignored.
!core/native/prebuilt/
core/native/prebuilt/*
!core/native/prebuilt/libnativemod-*.so
core/native/prebuilt/*-dbg.so
!core/native/prebuilt/libmain_needed-*.bin
